## 2026-03-27 - PublishPanel: varCorrelationIdRef/varReadResolveRef shared ref concurrency bug
- Replaced single-slot `varCorrelationIdRef` + `varReadResolveRef` refs with a Map-based `varPendingRef` (keyed by unique correlation ID), matching the pattern already used in SyncPanel.tsx. Both `computeVarDiff` and `runReadinessChecks` now store their resolve callbacks independently in the Map, so concurrent calls no longer overwrite each other.
- Updated the `variables-read` message handler to look up the resolver by correlation ID from the Map instead of checking against a single ref.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/PublishPanel.tsx` ~L211 (ref declaration), ~L351 (computeVarDiff), ~L577 (runReadinessChecks), ~L413 (message handler)

